name: NFTcard_009_pixel edition///bouz
description:
Collection of cards about the artists and works in our NFT collections, created to spread the work of creators in the Tezos blockchain NFT community.

Each card contains the pseudonym or name of the artist, his Twitter user, a work with his title and #OBJKT, the profile that the artist has on his Twitter or website and the most relevant tags used in his works, number of creations and number of collectors, finally there are some values ​​that we have created and they are the following:

The value in the upper left corner is called ENERGY (monthly average of minted works)

The value in the heart called the POWER of LOVE (collections / creations)

In total the first collection will be 33 different works from 33 different creators, every 8 normal cards will be followed by a mini special edition from three different creators that have something in common (technique, country, movement, etc) these special editions will only have 333 editions , at the same value of the other 33NFTcards 0.033 Tezos

The resources obtained will be used to buy more creations in NFT and to be able to continue with more NFTcards, the goal is to make 333 cards in 10 series of 33. 10% of the editions will be reserved to give away to the NFT Community and promote the creation and collection of NFTs.
